comments.en: This ontology models the knowledge related to cities and their tourist and business attractions. It allows the description of localities, services, and events in each city.

comment.en: Hotel enity focused on beach accommodations.
Restaurant entity that serves mexican food.
Event entity focused on cultural activities.
Transport entity that provides bus service for the public.
Restaurant entity that serves japanese food.
Hotel enity focused on turistic accommodations.
In principle any thing can be a Tourist Attraction located in a city, from a Museums and Monuments to a Parks. Its quality is rated.
Attraction entity reperesenting a natural shoreline by the sea.
Transport entity that provides tram service for the public.
Enity that represents an occasion of public interest in a city at a specific date.
